data.name: Label18.Text
data.value: These are your RGB Trackers. They are Located at Approximatly Half way down the Program Forum in the tab named 'Colour Generator'. These are used to track your Red, Green and Blue Colour Values. These are the 3 Primary colours. The Maximum Value Each Tracker Can go to is 255. You can make Millions of Colours using this System. Please Proceed to the next page by pressing 'Next Page'
